    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to be roadworthy again. The engine struggles to idle and shows signs of a head gasket leak, while the transmission shifts harshly under load. Externally, there is pervasive rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with multiple deep scratches and faded paint across the roof. The interior has seen better days, with several tears in the upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and non-functioning air conditioning. This car is recommended for a buyer looking for a major project or a source for parts, and it is sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 3800.0,
