    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine currently has significant trouble staying running at idle, and the transmission requires a full inspection as it is not engaging properly. Externally, there is visible rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches and dents across the body. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn seats and a non-functional climate control system. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
